{"tid":1138600,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想轉做紀律部隊 回饋社會 保護市民","createTime":"2019-05-04T15:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T17:26:56.000Z","uid":90802,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d67d54a29aaeb310c480f432accda0a22d8457f9","tid":1138600,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"天生性格就好鐘意幫人 保護弱小<br />\n一直以黎，身邊有比人恰會發聲，唔公道嘅事會企出黎，遇到困難會幫手解決，你唔開心會聽你慎。<br />\n見到人地解決到問題而笑個下就係對我最大嘅感謝，見到人開心我就開心。<br />\n即使而加出黎做野仍然參加義工，探訪獨居老人，路宿者同社區中心幫手。<br />\n<br />\n而加份工係ok，家人鐘意朋友羡慕，但對人生冇乜意義，感覺好似為做而做咁，想得到金錢之外嘅野。人生閱歷少諗野可能比較天真，將來或者變成仆街自私害人嘅食屎狗，但想變質之前，盡最大所能去幫助社會有需要嘅人。所以有諗過轉做警察or救護，不過人工會少咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係連登仔有冇工種介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e932c2bffb362d32b2bb14e68de7c177052b70d","tid":1138600,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d9beab782759c757229b53907c970c32e3fa2967","tid":1138600,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T15:41:16.000Z","msg":"師姐想做散定係做幫辦？"},{"pid":"fc21f67c6089994e8d80d792c8aa6118ff592b28","tid":1138600,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"樓主有玩sport不如同我打返場友誼波先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我最鐘意格鬥型"},{"pid":"81f281b702e857374f99c3202b8d2f92c75cfe9a","tid":1138600,"uid":138522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"98a2dd6d98dd5b13683f933cc6850c7a63c6b13f","tid":1138600,"uid":83594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"咁你有冇為左乜野唔公道既事而企出黎?"},{"pid":"e50636dbc797517a146bd473072aee424e2f8700","tid":1138600,"uid":6371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"幫人有好多方法 唔一定要做警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  況且你入職之後既工作絕對唔係你宜家諗咁樣去盡力幫人定點<br />\n<br />\n你fg人工可以高過差佬 前景差極有限啦 某程度上做工程都可以幫到人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第時你有番咁上下經驗、能力、收入，就有更多途經、資源去用你既方法幫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6987bbe0577ba5098d04f11465fa876bd597d696","tid":1138600,"uid":11895,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"仲有人覺得黑警係除暴安良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8909444a3519011a2dfc9e198080f5295c9eda5c","tid":1138600,"uid":126384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"想做咪做囉 後悔可以走"},{"pid":"20b2b6d484df231a2d08996ada2762e15d729ad8","tid":1138600,"uid":214534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">督察就話姐 <br />\n散仔就唔好喇</span>"}]}